milestoneDTO Data Type

Namespace
(Default)
Properties
name data type type namespace min/max occurs description
actions actionInfoDTO element 0/unbounded The list of actions available to the caller for execution.
created dateTime element 0/1 The date the milestone was created.
date dateTime element 0/1 The date of the milestone. This is the date the user selects when creating the milestone (not the created date).
description textContentDTO element 0/1 A description of the milestone.
id int element 0/1 The ID of the milestone.
inc_id int element 0/1 The incident to which this milestone belongs.
inc_name string element 0/1 The name of the incident to which this milestone belongs.
inc_owner objectHandle element 0/1 The owner of the incident to which this milestone belongs.
perms milestonePermsDTO element 0/1 An object that describes the current user's permissions on the milestone.
title string element 0/1 The title of the milestone.
user justUserDTO element 0/1 An object that describes the user who created the milestone.

Example

<milestoneDTO>
  <id>...</id>
  <title>...</title>
  <description>
    <format>...</format>
    <content>...</content>
  </description>
  <user>
    <id>...</id>
    <fname>...</fname>
    <lname>...</lname>
    <status>...</status>
    <email>...</email>
    <phone>...</phone>
    <cell>...</cell>
    <title>...</title>
    <notes>...</notes>
    <last_login>...</last_login>
    <locked>...</locked>
    <is_external>...</is_external>
  </user>
  <created>...</created>
  <inc_id>...</inc_id>
  <inc_name>...</inc_name>
  <inc_owner>
    <id>...</id>
    <name>...</name>
  </inc_owner>
  <perms>
    <update>...</update>
    <delete>...</delete>
  </perms>
  <date>...</date>
  <actions>
    <id>...</id>
    <name>...</name>
    <enabled>...</enabled>
  </actions>
</milestoneDTO>
